  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 -\u00a0 \u00a0\u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb9\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ruling party did not give those who voted against emergency an opportunity to express their views - Alleged ruling party member Kodaheva",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Members of the ruling party who voted against the emergency law were not given an opportunity to comment on the parliamentary debate on it. However, history will decide whether the decision we have taken is right,\" said ruling party member of parliament Prof. Nalakka Kodaheva.",
        "He said this while referring to the decision to vote against the emergency bill in Parliament.",
        "The debate on the emergency bill took place in Parliament last Wednesday. Some members of the ruling party had decided to vote against the motion.",
        "We have asked the Chief Whip of the House of Commons for time to explain why they are voting against it and to give them an opportunity to comment on the impact of imposing emergency legislation on the current situation.",
        "However, he said that there is no room for anyone to comment against the Emergency Act in the discussion.",
        "Even ordinary law was abused in the good governance government and measures were taken to suppress political dissidents on a large scale.",
        "In the hands of rulers with such a track record, it would be very appalling to give life like Emergency. That is why I voted against the Emergency Act.",
        "And allowing the government to create an enabling environment to suppress all forms of protest under the guise of emergency law is an affront to the people's representative. So history will judge whether our decision to vote against the Emergency Act was right."
      ],
